article_text: With more than 150 buildings letting you in to check out hidden treasures and learn more about the city and its history, Doors Open Milwaukee kicked off today. Historic Milwaukee Inc. organizes the annual visual scavenger hunt, with ticketed tours available. Tours continue tomorrow from 10 a.m. to 5 p.m.
